{% extends "email/_base.html.j2" %}
{% block title %}You Now Have Access to Track Construction Progress — {{ project_name }}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="greeting">Dear {{ first_name }},</div>

<p><strong>{{ developer_name }}</strong> has given you access to BuildTrack to monitor construction progress on <strong>{{ project_name }}</strong>.</p>

<p>BuildTrack gives you a permanent, verified record of every construction update throughout your build. You can check progress at any time without needing to contact the sales team.</p>

<div class="datacard">
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Your project page is live now at:</strong><br>
    <a href="{{ project_url }}" style="color: #14B8A6; text-decoration: none;">{{ project_url }}</a></p>
</div>

<p>To access your private buyer portal, click the link below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{ portal_link }}" class="btn">Access Buyer Portal</a>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<p style="font-weight: 600; color: #f1f5f9;">What you will find on your portal:</p>
<ul style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; margin-left: 20px;">
    <li>GPS-verified construction photos from the site</li>
    <li>Five-stage milestone progress tracker</li>
    <li>Verified construction update records, permanently archived</li>
    <li>Automatic notifications whenever a new update is approved</li>
</ul>

<p>Your access is private. No other buyer can see your name or details on the platform.</p>

<p>If you have any questions about your portal, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@buildtrack.co.ke" style="color: #14B8A6; text-decoration: none;">support@buildtrack.co.ke</a>.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">The BuildTrack Team<br>
<a href="https://buildtrack.co.ke" style="color: #14B8A6; text-decoration: none;">buildtrack.co.ke</a></p>
{% endblock %}
